{"type": "article", "id": 23106, "title": "圆锥扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-02T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145823VvIMhHs5YaZb2iCj.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个可改变大小的扬声器，它是圆锥形的。沿着中轴可以将它卷起来以放大或缩小扬声器，以此来调整音量的大小，是简单而有趣的设计，它回归了改变音量大小的原理。设计师出身于韩国，目前在美国就学，产品受到 nendo 的启发，目前还是一个概念。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021458194GAxZCHkRIKEOBsN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145820b1v5slwdUXR7Qh9j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145821vzPclId7an4XSRKi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145821gDvSyx9Tz20afuqd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145822vj8ieltcgWKdMbas.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}